    "causal_summary": "Graph-Augmented Retrieval adds a knowledge-graph layer to the Hybrid RAG Fusion pipeline. Rather than treating the graph as a first-class ranker from day one, this phase adopts a **sparse-first** posture: typed 1-hop expansion by default, communities only when density justifies it, and deterministic save-time enrichment that keeps the graph fresh without runtime LLM calls.",
